{"tid":1943595,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美專家談向中國索賠的法理依據","createTime":"2020-03-25T21:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T02:21:20.000Z","uid":141151,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ad697eb949a31cf73f33b23fb89df73ede9ade83","tid":1943595,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T21:21:07.000Z","msg":"美專家談向中國索賠的法理依據<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200325-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%AB%98%E8%AA%BF%E5%90%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B4%A2%E8%B3%A0%E7%9A%84%E6%B3%95%E7%90%86%E4%BE%9D%E6%93%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20200325-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%25AB%2598%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E5%2590%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E8%25B3%25A0%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E4%25BE%259D%25E6%2593%259A&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4Rq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=0480c630\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200325-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%AB%98%E8%AA%BF%E5%90%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B4%A2%E8%B3%A0%E7%9A%84%E6%B3%95%E7%90%86%E4%BE%9D%E6%93%9A</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>繼美國地方機構提案上訴中國之後，美國國會參眾兩院周二也提出議案，要求調查中國對新冠疫情的處理方式，並且要求中方對各國的損失進行賠償。美方提出索賠要求的法律依據是什麼？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">美國海軍戰爭學院的海洋法和政策學教授詹姆斯&bull;拉斯卡（James Kraska）周二公布了一份研究性文章，文章指出，各國完全可以通過國際法現有的框架對中國政府或者是中國共產黨的不負責任的行為提出起訴。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n文章指出，2002年中國政府隱瞞薩斯疫情導致病毒蔓延至 28個國家，死亡總數為774人。雖然同今天的新冠疫情相對比，薩斯病毒所造成的受害者的規模要小得多。但是，他使全球各國都意識到隱瞞病情所可能導致的嚴重後果。世界衛生組織因此在2005年通過了國際衛生條例，條例特別提到涉及薩斯SARS以及&ldquo;由新亞型引起的類似疾病&rdquo;（如引起COVID-19的病毒），世衛組織成員國有義務&ldquo;在24小時內在世界衛生組織內共享相關信息&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n而很明顯，無論中國政府對世衛組織有多大的影響力，無論北京如何控制世衛組織領導人的聲明，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國政府並沒有遵守2005年通過的具有法律約束性的條例的規定。</span></span></strong>武漢醫生李文良的故事清楚地說明，中國政府並未在24小時內對外通報，不僅如此，那些敢於對外披露信息的人還遭到打壓。而倘若北京政府按規定公布新冠病毒的信息，將可以挽救成千上萬人的生命。"},{"pid":"4b0103ffb7a85df6f1fd91e9cb213b64aac9362f","tid":1943595,"uid":147944,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T21:24:52.000Z","msg":"可唔可以順便告鳩埋支衛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班撚樣貪貪埋埋唔少"},{"pid":"9e1c19bf2c4df8d38f64829228b3531a56a70035","tid":1943595,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T22:01:50.000Z","msg":"唉 美國到底幾時做野"},{"pid":"8126c8cdb4114ece4a37348c0a5408661c0219c4","tid":1943595,"uid":24730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T22:14:11.000Z","msg":"唔該美帝要求支共割讓香港"},{"pid":"f00d57b6820e74fde4b9add06e1cf7b53b904b67","tid":1943595,"uid":193834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T22:15:32.000Z","msg":"美國堅持正名<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">武漢病毒</span></span>但其它國家反對 G7一致同意：中國散播疫情假消息<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/realtimenews/article/new/20200326/1723842/papersec_right\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20200326%2F1723842%2Fpapersec_right&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4Rq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=d7ffb6f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20200326%2F1723842%2Fpapersec_right&h=93e44bdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/realtimenews/article/new/20200326/1723842/papersec_right</a><br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】蓬佩奧：G7外長同意中國正散播虛假消息 企圖轉移視線<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200326/EKTJQCYMM26GWYPDWAHT7JA63E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200326%2FEKTJQCYMM26GWYPDWAHT7JA63E%2F&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4Rq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=1d65625b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200326%2FEKTJQCYMM26GWYPD